timeline.bodyText:
I prefer not explicitly testing long strings of text and instead labeling those passages with an aria-label and testing for that. That way we can make minor changes to the text content without having to worry about the tests. I recommend adding:
aria-label={'customEntityTitle'}
and then check like so:
expect(getByLabelText('customEntityTitle')).toBeInTheDocument();

